      "cookedHtml": "<p>Please post your reviews, feedback, issues, questions about the “Drive Connect” app here.</p>\n<p>This powerful app connects your <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> workspace with OneDrive, enabling you to upload, preview, and manage files directly from your boards without switching between platforms.</p>\n<p>See it in action! <a href=\"https://calendly.com/atul31gupta\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Schedule a demo</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Key Features of OneDrive Integration with <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/outbox_tray.png?v=12\" title=\":outbox_tray:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":outbox_tray:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Upload Files to OneDrive from <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Seamlessly upload files like documents, images, spreadsheets, and presentations to OneDrive directly from <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/point_right.png?v=12\" title=\":point_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":point_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Stay on track by managing everything in one place without leaving the platform!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/arrows_counterclockwise.png?v=12\" title=\":arrows_counterclockwise:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":arrows_counterclockwise:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Automatic Sync</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/stopwatch.png?v=12\" title=\":stopwatch:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":stopwatch:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Stay updated in real-time! Changes made to documents are instantly synced between <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> and OneDrive.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Everyone on the team will always be on the same page—no more outdated files!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/card_index_dividers.png?v=12\" title=\":card_index_dividers:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":card_index_dividers:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Organize and Manage Files Efficiently</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/file_folder.png?v=12\" title=\":file_folder:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":file_folder:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Automatically create board-level and item-level folders in OneDrive.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/dart.png?v=12\" title=\":dart:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":dart:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Effortlessly organize your files, create new folders, and manage everything directly from <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/handshake.png?v=12\" title=\":handshake:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":handshake:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Real-Time Collaboration</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/speech_balloon.png?v=12\" title=\":speech_balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":speech_balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Collaborate on Word Docs, Excel Sheets, and PowerPoint presentations without leaving <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/link.png?v=12\" title=\":link:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":link:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Share files with your team and experience real-time updates—boosting productivity like never before!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/closed_lock_with_key.png?v=12\" title=\":closed_lock_with_key:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":closed_lock_with_key:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Backup &amp; Security</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/shield.png?v=12\" title=\":shield:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":shield:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Enjoy the robust backup and security features of OneDrive.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/busts_in_silhouette.png?v=12\" title=\":busts_in_silhouette:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":busts_in_silhouette:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Control access to sensitive data and ensure your files remain safe and secure within your workspace.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Take your productivity to the next level with this seamless integration!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/open_book.png?v=12\" title=\":open_book:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":open_book:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Need More Details?</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/mag.png?v=12\" title=\":mag:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":mag:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Check out our <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/e/2PACX-1vS6adC-Uhaja6YZbrLvypZkVJDP7_EvozfZ-4asFTDIIfJWxr93xRIhlPmviDjug_HzNhb573ivtwx_/pub\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">complete app documentation</a> for in-depth guidance</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/point_right.png?v=12\" title=\":point_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":point_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Get started today and unlock your full potential!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/speech_balloon.png?v=12\" title=\":speech_balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":speech_balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> For any feedback, suggestions, or queries, please contact us at <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/email.png?v=12\" title=\":email:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":email:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> [apps@cloudvandana.com](mailto: <a href=\"mailto:apps@cloudvandana.com\">apps@cloudvandana.com</a>)</p>"
