      "cookedHtml": "<h3><a name=\"p-228067-uploadogydvmjhloqe2uuzoztnzqmb7ikpng-new-feature-alert-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228067-uploadogydvmjhloqe2uuzoztnzqmb7ikpng-new-feature-alert-1\"></a><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/d/ad038df615da43bb0d0893f61a41f44aff56b10a.png\" alt=\"🎉\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /> New Feature Alert!</h3>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228067-automate-your-onedrive-workflow-in-mondaycomhttpmondaycom-with-onedrive-connecthttpschieb-zcmpmaillist-managecomclick112de226f8c48d8c1112de226f8c48d532-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228067-automate-your-onedrive-workflow-in-mondaycomhttpmondaycom-with-onedrive-connecthttpschieb-zcmpmaillist-managecomclick112de226f8c48d8c1112de226f8c48d532-2\"></a>Automate Your OneDrive Workflow in <a href=\"http://monday.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> with <a href=\"https://chieb-zcmp.maillist-manage.com/click/112de226f8c48d8c1/112de226f8c48d532\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">OneDrive Connect</a></h3>\n<p>Good news! <a href=\"https://chieb-zcmp.maillist-manage.com/click/112de226f8c48d8c1/112de226f8c48d534\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">OneDrive Connect</a> now features powerful Automations (Recipes) to streamline your file management in <a href=\"http://monday.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a>.</p>\n<p>Here’s what you can automate:</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228067-uploadqgrmqol2myfntutjmctoli9gxqvpng-auto-upload-files-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228067-uploadqgrmqol2myfntutjmctoli9gxqvpng-auto-upload-files-3\"></a><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/8/b8144f5d66988060e74326ea12e0f5b0ff74750b.png\" alt=\"📄\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /> Auto-upload files</h3>\n<p>Automatically transfer files from <a href=\"http://monday.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> columns to designated OneDrive folders based on your set triggers.</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228067-upload2lmcjnkxqlbqah99kuwj131gdgjpng-auto-create-folders-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228067-upload2lmcjnkxqlbqah99kuwj131gdgjpng-auto-create-folders-4\"></a><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/1/3/136b249a2ebacc585031b838e0d30a7397701c7f.png\" alt=\"📂\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /> Auto-create folders</h3>\n<p>Automatically generate OneDrive folders in sync with new items or modifications on your <a href=\"http://monday.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> boards.</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228067-upload6qcy44z5vcsppnm3zgbp62w6mcupng-time-saving-automation-5\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228067-upload6qcy44z5vcsppnm3zgbp62w6mcupng-time-saving-automation-5\"></a><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/0/3000060038ed7b52a5e474ede51650848bdb23f4.png\" alt=\"⏱️\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /> Time-Saving Automation</h3>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228067-h-6\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228067-h-6\"></a></h3>\n<p>Eliminate manual work and focus on what matters most instead of getting bogged down in file management.</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228067-uploadybsg9cuapbsm8zszjdjbmviqyiipng-powerful-yet-simple-recipes7-7\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228067-uploadybsg9cuapbsm8zszjdjbmviqyiipng-powerful-yet-simple-recipes7-7\"></a><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/f/2/f291f5256a6cb878578c11c8816f3e15ee3be2fa.png\" alt=\"🚀\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /> Powerful, Yet Simple Recipes(7+)</h3>\n<p>Automate file transfers with intuitive integration recipes that require minimal setup.</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228067-uploadenhkcjiuahulakhzlyfmiuxz3vmpng-highly-customizable-actions5-8\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228067-uploadenhkcjiuahulakhzlyfmiuxz3vmpng-highly-customizable-actions5-8\"></a><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/7/67b08070fea81a33d851f49f4f9426f29d594dac.png\" alt=\"🛠️\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /> Highly Customizable Actions(5+)</h3>\n<p>Combine custom actions with any <a href=\"http://monday.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> trigger to automate exactly what you need.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/c/0c2f73207c8c6ef51b5b2972c12fda9ea5f8dbcf.jpeg\" title=\"OneDrive Connect All Recipes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/c/0c2f73207c8c6ef51b5b2972c12fda9ea5f8dbcf_2_690x388.jpeg\" alt=\"OneDrive Connect All Recipes\" width=\"690\" height=\"388\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">OneDrive Connect All Recipes</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×1080 103 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Need help getting started?</p>\n<p>We provide dedicated support to set up <a href=\"https://chieb-zcmp.maillist-manage.com/click/112de226f8c48d8c1/112de226f8c48d538\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">OneDrive Connect</a> for your specific needs. If you’d like personalized assistance, please feel free to <a href=\"https://chieb-zcmp.maillist-manage.com/click/112de226f8c48d8c1/112de226f8c48d53a\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">schedule a call</a>.</p>\n<p>Start saving time with <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000702/onedrive-connect\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">OneDrive Connect</a> Automations today!</p>"
